  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Roadmap</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2568620/extras/c443e4868140fe70de4b184ece53ae7e.apng?t=1767179222\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2568620/extras/c443e4868140fe70de4b184ece53ae7e.poster.avif?t=1767179222\" class=\"bb_img\" width=576 height=288 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Future updates to <i>Fakeway</i> will continue to enhance agriculture, circuitry, automation, and online multiplayer experiences. We hope that through continuous content expansion, the game will gradually evolve into a world with deeper systems and creative space, rather than simply a pixel survival game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We plan to develop a process with 10 bosses, and we have completed 4 so far. In 2016, we plan to complete the development of all game content.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In 2017, we plan to optimize the details of the entire game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Introduction</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2568620/extras/6d24f13f95c0e10ab4e9701a225b936f.poster.avif?t=1767179222\" width=1170 height=379 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2568620/extras/6d24f13f95c0e10ab4e9701a225b936f.webm?t=1767179222\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Connection: Currently you can connect via Steam or LAN.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2568620/extras/3605aa4655a3a1e77617d91d808c42ff.poster.avif?t=1767179222\" width=1170 height=379 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2568620/extras/3605aa4655a3a1e77617d91d808c42ff.webm?t=1767179222\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combat: Including melee weapons, long-range weapons, staff summons, and other weapons. Currently, it contains 30 common monsters and 5 bosses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2568620/extras/08e45cec455a5de272125ab3665f9a44.poster.avif?t=1767179222\" width=1170 height=379 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2568620/extras/08e45cec455a5de272125ab3665f9a44.webm?t=1767179222\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Planting: Plant various crops. Currently there are more than 10 plants that can be planted.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2568620/extras/0672350a739ece99c95c1f5275a42a37.poster.avif?t=1767179222\" width=1170 height=379 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2568620/extras/0672350a739ece99c95c1f5275a42a37.webm?t=1767179222\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exploration: Currently includes villages, forests, dungeons, oceans and other landforms. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collection: Items dropped by monsters, collected items, mined items, and synthesized items are worth collecting. There are currently 350 items of various types.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Construction: Build a camp to accommodate the arrival of NPCs. Currently, wooden houses, wooden tables, and wooden chairs can be built. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you like Terraria, you can try this game. It will bring you a different experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Feedback</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2568620/extras/7b533f8b4056bd6f541a456cb199279f.apng?t=1767179222\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2568620/extras/7b533f8b4056bd6f541a456cb199279f.poster.avif?t=1767179222\" class=\"bb_img\" width=288 height=96 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2568620/extras/e7e6708bcd9dbfd1e8754ff16677b829.avif?t=1767179222\" width=558 height=134 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple feedback channels are available on the game homepage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Another anonymous feedback tool is built into the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We appreciate the sharp criticism more than positive reviews.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Roadmap</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2568620/extras/c443e4868140fe70de4b184ece53ae7e.apng?t=1767179222\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2568620/extras/c443e4868140fe70de4b184ece53ae7e.poster.avif?t=1767179222\" class=\"bb_img\" width=576 height=288 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Future updates to <i>Fakeway</i> will continue to enhance agriculture, circuitry, automation, and online multiplayer experiences. We hope that through continuous content expansion, the game will gradually evolve into a world with deeper systems and creative space, rather than simply a pixel survival game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We plan to develop a process with 10 bosses, and we have completed 4 so far. In 2016, we plan to complete the development of all game content.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In 2017, we plan to optimize the details of the entire game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Introduction</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2568620/extras/6d24f13f95c0e10ab4e9701a225b936f.poster.avif?t=1767179222\" width=1170 height=379 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2568620/extras/6d24f13f95c0e10ab4e9701a225b936f.webm?t=1767179222\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Connection: Currently you can connect via Steam or LAN.</p><p class=\"bb_paragr