=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exploration: Currently includes villages, forests, dungeons, oceans and other landforms. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collection: Items dropped by monsters, collected items, mined items, and synthesized items are worth collecting. There are currently 350 items of various types.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Construction: Build a camp to accommodate the arrival of NPCs. Currently, wooden houses, wooden tables, and wooden chairs can be built. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you like Terraria, you can try this game. It will bring you a different experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Feedback</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2568620/extras/7b533f8b4056bd6f541a456cb199279f.apng?t=1767179222\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2568620/extras/7b533f8b4056bd6f541a456cb199279f.poster.avif?t=1767179222\" class=\"bb_img\" width=288 height=96 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2568620/extras/e7e6708bcd9dbfd1e8754ff16677b829.avif?t=1767179222\" width=558 height=134 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple feedback channels are available on the game homepage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Another anonymous feedback tool is built into the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We appreciate the sharp criticism more than positive reviews.</p>",
